Class MainActivity

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      com.cs.pausis.MainActivity

public class MainActivity
extends Activity

This is the Main Activity class that facilitates the receipt of all user inputs into the application. It's associated view contains all the necessary controls that will help to get the inputs from the user.
